{"ops":[{"insert":"基本用途"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"这是一个基于 Vue.js 框架（使用 TypeScript 和 vue-property-decorator 装饰器语法）编写的 **分割线（Divider）组件**，名为 `monitor-divider`。它的主要用途是在用户界面中渲染一条水平的分割线，用于视觉上分隔不同的内容区块，提升界面的可读性与美观性。\n\n主要功能"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"\n1. 渲染一条水平分割线\n   - 组件本质上是一个高度为 0 的块级元素，通过 CSS 的 `border-bottom` 属性绘制出一条水平的实线，用作视觉分隔。\n\n2. 支持自定义样式属性\n   - 线宽（width）：控制分割线的粗细，默认值为 `1px`。\n   - 外边距（margin）：控制分割线上下左右的间距，默认是 `'16px 20px'`，即上下 16px，左右 20px。\n   - 颜色（color）：控制分割线的颜色，默认是浅灰色 `#e0e0e0`。\n\n使用方法"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"plain"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"<template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  <div>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    <p>这是第一部分内容</p>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    <monitor-divider />"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    <p>这是第二部分内容，与第一部分被分割线隔开</p>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  </div>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"</template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"<script lang=\"ts\">"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"import { Component, Vue } from 'vue-property-decorator';"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"import Divider from './divider.vue'; // 确保路径正确"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"@Component({"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  components: {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    MonitorDivider: Divider, // 如果你在模板中用的是 <monitor-divider />"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  },"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"})"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"export default class YourComponent extends Vue {}"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"</script>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"\n> 注意：由于原组件使用了 `@Component({ name: 'monitor-divider' })`，因此在模板中可以直接使用 `<monitor-divider />` 标签。如果你想使用其他标签名（如 `<MonitorDivider />`），则需要在注册时做映射，如上例所示。\n\n自定义分割线样式（可选）"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"\n你可以通过传递 `props` 来定制分割线的外观：\n\n- width（Number，可选）：分割线的粗细，默认为 `1`（即 1px）。\n- margin（String，可选）：分割线的外边距，接受标准的 CSS margin 值，如 `'10px 0'`，默认为 `'16px 20px'`。\n- color（String，可选）：分割线的颜色，支持任何有效的 CSS 颜色值，如 `'#ccc'`、`'red'` 或 `'rgba(0,0,0,0.1)'`，默认为 `'#e0e0e0'`。\n\n"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"plain"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"<template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  <div>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    <p>内容区域 A</p>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    <!-- 自定义分割线：线宽 2px，颜色为深灰色，外边距上下 20px -->"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    <monitor-divider :width=\"2\" :color=\"'#999'\" :margin=\"'20px 0'\" />"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    <p>内容区域 B</p>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"plain"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  </div>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"</template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"<script lang=\"ts\">"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"import { Component, Vue } from 'vue-property-decorator';"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"import Divider from './divider.vue';"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"@Component({"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  components: {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    MonitorDivider: Divider,"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  },"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"})"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"export default class YourComponent extends Vue {}"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"</script>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"\n如需进一步增强，也可以考虑支持垂直分割线、虚线样式、响应式行为等扩展功能。\n"}],"extra":{"updator":"Austin","update_at":"2026-01-21 14:43:25"}}